ght)."},{"content":"Once set, turn out of cups or moulds and serve straight from the freezer."}],"hintsAndTricks":["If you can't find popsicle sticks you can use spoons instead or for an added treat, candy canes.","Reserve your egg whites to use in one of the pavlova stack recipes.","These individual ice creams are the perfect festive treat on a hot Christmas day."],"basicInfo":["medium","10m","12h","12 portions"]}